snippet.title: Vault - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Vault is a spooky, atmospheric exploration game. Uncover the story of a mysterious island through the lens of a primitive drone as you search for the artifact concealed within it, and avoid the guardian of the island.

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/NPnaERQQSy
On Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3062080/Vault/
On Itch: https://keveatscheese.itch.io/vaultsteam
